181 West Madison is a property experience platform that manages all of the daily activities in a building for both staff and occupants, enhancing engagement, driving value and increasing retention. With the 181 West Madison app, occupants and staff can eliminate many of the manual processes including:

• Visitor Management
• Package Delivery
• Service Requests/Work Order Management
• Amenity Reservations
• Curated Vendors and Exclusive Deals
• Valet & Taxi Requests
• Payments
• Community Newsfeed, Groups, Events, Polls, & Building Updates
• Marketplace
• Direct & Group Messaging
• Document Vault
• Customized commonly used websites and resources for occupants
• And much more!

Contact us at support@risebuildings.com for any questions about the app!
